source.name: SAFER - Company Snapshot - SAFER - Company Snapshot
source.description: The Company Snapshot is a concise electronic record of company identification, size, commodity information, and safety record, including the safety rating (if any), a roadside out-of-service inspection summary, and crash information. The Company Snapshot is available via an ad-hoc query (one carrier at a time) free of charge.
